metadata.name: Outrageous Influence
metadata.description:
Outrageous influence, a force so strong,  
It can sway us left or right,  
It can make us do what's right,  
Or lead us down a path of fright.

It can be a voice in our ear,  
Whispering words of temptation,  
It can be a pressure to conform,  
To fit in with a certain nation.

Outrageous influence, it can be good,  
Encouraging us to rise above,  
But it can also be destructive,  
Leading us to act out of love.

We must be careful of its power,  
And choose our influences wisely,  
For they can shape our future,  
And determine our destiny.

So let us strive to be true to ourselves,  
And resist the pull of outrageous influence,  
For in the end, it is our own choices,  
That determine our path, and our precedence.
